    <item>
      <title>Neovim and journey of coding</title>
      <link>https://nainablog.vercel.app/posts/my-new-post/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 12:52:34 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>Ijadux2</author>
      <guid>https://nainablog.vercel.app/posts/my-new-post/</guid>
      <description>&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;neovim&#34; --&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;Neovim
  &lt;a href=&#34;#neovim&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor-link&#34;&gt;
&lt;svg
    xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;
    width=&#34;1rem&#34; height=&#34;1rem&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;
    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;
    stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;
    &lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;9&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;15&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;15&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;10&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;8&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;16&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;14&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i use neovim for most for the time in my laptop.
using archlinux with Noctalia shell, custome plugins and config&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ijadux2/sharingan.nvim&#34;&gt;Sharingan.nvim&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;my neovim consist of&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;plugin managaer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;theme {catppuccin-mocha}&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;my custome plugins {git,app-launcher,tangle,etc}&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;github plugins&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;my fav. snacks.nvim&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;and many more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;just not becasue of plugins i like neovim
i like becasue of speed and terminal based editor&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
